messages.content:
what's the word when you want to make something super precice and exacting? I have an app that makes an average guess for all the prayers someone missed in their life and then there's a button i was thinking about calling "get specific" or "specify prayers" i want 7 different names that imply that they can click this button to get a more granular view of all the prayers they missed so instead of 50 percent for all prayers you can say for morning prayer on average i prayed only 20 percent but in midday i prayed 80 percent because i was at school and we all prayed together
what should that button be called?

1. "Fine-Tune Prayers"
2. "Detailed Breakdown"
3. "Precision Mode"
4. "Specific Analysis"
5. "Granular Insights"
6. "Refine Prayer Data"
7. "Customize Prayer Records"
